RSEFRLG.textGreet_rse: When I was young, I traveled the worldŇas a POKéMON TRAINER.
RSEFRLG.textGreet_frlg: I may not look like much now,Ňbut when I was younger…
RSEFRLG.textMoveBox_rs: ȆÀËOh, of course, I have to unlockŇthe door!
RSEFRLG.textMoveBox_frlg: ȆÀËOh, of course, I have to moveŇthe boxes!
RSEFRLG.textMoveBox_e: ȆÀËOh, of course, I have to moveŇthe plants!
RSEFRLG.textWeHere: ȆÀËLOOKER: I am here in Hoenn to findŇthe leader MAXIE.ȼAs well, I am helping my friendŇProfessor FENNEL.ȼThis is why you are here, no?ŇI shall tell her you are ready.ŞCome! Allons y!
RSEFRLG.textWeHere_em: ȆÀËLOOKER: I am here in Hoenn to findŇthe leaders MAXIE and ARCHIE.ȼAs well, I am helping my friendŇProfessor FENNEL.ȼThis is why you are here, no?ŇI shall tell her you are ready.ŞCome! Allons y!
RSEFRLG.textRecieved: ȆÀÁƲÀ’S POKéMON were sent to theŇPC!
RSEFRLG.textYouMustBe_first: Ah! You must be ƲÀ!ŇI was told you’d be coming.ȼOh! I still wear my disguise! Pardon!ŇOr, rather, let me introduce myself.
RSEFRLG.textYouMustBe_second: Ah, ƲÀ! Welcome back!ŇGood to see you again!ȼOh! I still wear my disguise! Pardon!
RSEFRLG.textIAm_first: ȆÀËI am a globe-trotting elite of theŇInternational Police.ȼMy name…ŞAh, no, I shall inform you of myŇcode name only.ȼMy code name, it is LOOKER!
RSEFRLG.textIAm_second: ȆÀËIt is I, globe-trotting elite of theŇInternational Police.ȼMy code name, it is LOOKER!
RSEFRLG.textPCConvo: ȆÀÉFENNEL: Ah, LOOKER! I take itŇƲÀ has arrived?ȼȆÀËLOOKER: Indeed! They’re ready toŇreceive their POKéMON!ȼȆÀÉFENNEL: Excellent! I’ll send themŇover momentarily… stand by!
RSEFRLG.textPCThanks: ȆÀÉFENNEL: It looks like everything wasŇsent to your PC successfully!ȼThank you both for your help!
RSEFRLG.textThank: ȆÀËThanks for stopping by, ƲÀ!ȼIf you’ll excuse me, I must returnŇto my disguise.ŞUntil our paths cross again!
RSEFRLG.textPCFull: ȆÀÉFENNEL: It seems like the PC is full!ȼGo make some room, and I can sendŇover the rest of your POKéMON.
RSEFRLG.textLookerFull: ȆÀËLOOKER: Speak to me again afterŇyou’ve made room, ƲÀ!ȼIn the meantime, I will return toŇmy disguise.

PTGB.DIA_OPEN: Hey there! I’m Professor Fennel. AsŇyou can see, I’m a scientist. InŇfact, the subject I’m researching isŇTrainers!ȼMy dream is to collect save files ofŇvarious trainers, but I haven’t hadŇany breakthroughs yet...ȼSo in the meantime, I’ve been workingŇon a different project with one of myŇold friends!ȼIn my home region, there’s a locationŇthat can make a Pokémon’s dreams intoŇreality.ȼThis means that any other PokémonŇthey meet in their dreams becomeŇreal!ȼThat’s fantastic, but my goal is toŇdo the same- just with a trainer’sŇdream instead! That’s why I need yourŇhelp!ȼI want to bring as many Pokémon outŇof your dreams as possible!ȼThere’s just over 250 Pokémon I wantŇto catalogue in my Dream PokéDex- orŇDream Dex for short.ȼBut I’ll let you keep any Pokémon-Ňthey’re from your dreams after all!ȼOne last note, save data backups areŇrecommended- just on the off chanceŇthat something goes wrong!ŇI think that’s everything...ȼwhenever you’re ready to start, justŇlet me know!ƞ
PTGB.DIA_E4: Hi trainer! I’m thrilled you’veŇdecided to help with our research,Ňbut we need the best of the best!ȼCome back after you’ve beaten theŇElite Four and become the Champion!ƞ
PTGB.DIA_MG_FRLGE: Sorry trainer, one more thing to takeŇcare of before we can begin- you needŇto enable MYSTERY GIFT!ȼHead to the nearest Poké Mart andŇfill out the questionnaire asŇfollows: LINK TOGETHER WITH ALL.ȼAfter that, you should be all set toŇgo! See you soon!ƞ
PTGB.DIA_MG_RS: Sorry trainer, one more thing to takeŇcare of before we can begin- you needŇto enable MYSTERY EVENT!ȼHead to the PETALBURG Pokémon CenterŇand tell the man next to the PC:ŇMYSTERY EVENT IS EXCITING. AfterŇthat, you should be all set to go!ȼSee you soon!ƞ
PTGB.DIA_LETS_START: Perfect, that’s all the information IŇneed! Let’s get started!ƞ
PTGB.DIA_START: On a second Game Boy family system,Ňplease load the Game Boy Pokémon gameŇyou wish to transfer from.ȼIn your Game Boy Pokémon game, makeŇyour current box the one you want toŇtransfer from.ȼThen connect this Game Boy Advance toŇthe other Game Boy family systemŇusing a Game Boy Color link cable.ȼOnce you’re ready, press A on thisŇdevice, talk to the Cable ClubŇattendant, and then initiate a trade.ƞ
PTGB.DIA_NEW_DEX: It looks like there’s at least oneŇnew Pokémon here that isn’t in theŇDream Dex! I’ll give them somethingŇextra sweet as a reward for you both.ƞ
PTGB.DIA_NO_NEW_DEX: It doesn’t look like there’s anythingŇnew for your Dream Dex, but that’sŇokay! It’s important to confirmŇresearch results with multiple tests!ƞ
PTGB.DIA_SEND_FRIEND_KANTO: I’m going to send these Pokémon toŇone of my friends so that you canŇpick them up! They live just south ofŇthe Pokémon center on Seven Island!ƞ
PTGB.DIA_SEND_FRIEND_HOENN_RS: I’m going to send these Pokémon toŇone of my friends so that you canŇpick them up!ȼThey live just southeast of theŇPokémon center in Mossdeep City!ƞ
PTGB.DIA_SEND_FRIEND_HOENN_E: I’m going to send these Pokémon toŇone of my friends so that you canŇpick them up!ȼThey live just southeast of theŇPokémon center in Sootopolis City!ƞ
PTGB.DIA_THANK: Thank you so much for your help!ŇWhenever you want to transfer moreŇPokémon, just let me know! See youŇaround!ƞ
PTGB.DIA_MG_OTHER_EVENT: Hi Trainer! It looks like you have aŇdifferent event currently loaded.ŇThat’s no problem, but it will beŇoverwritten if you continue.ȼTurn off the system now if you wantŇto experience your current event, butŇotherwise-ƞ
PTGB.DIA_PKMN_TO_COLLECT: Hi Trainer! It looks like you stillŇhave Pokémon to pick up... I can’tŇsend over new Pokémon until you pickŇthose up.ȼCome back after you’ve received them!ƞ
PTGB.DIA_NO_VALID_PKMN: Sorry Trainer, it doesn’t look likeŇyou have any valid Pokémon in yourŇcurrent box right now.ȼGo double check your current box andŇwe can give it another shot!ƞ
PTGB.DIA_ASK_QUEST: Hi trainer! Before we begin, I needŇto ask you a few questions.ƞ
PTGB.DIA_WHAT_GAME_TRANS: And which Game Boy Pokémon game areŇyou transferring from?ƞ
PTGB.DIA_WHAT_LANG_TRANS: What language is the Game Boy PokémonŇgame that you’re transferring from?ƞ
PTGB.DIA_NO_GB_ROM: I’m sorry, but that version in thatŇlanguage is not currently supported.ƞ
PTGB.DIA_IN_BOX: Alright! Let’s take a look at theŇPokémon that will be transfered.ȼPlease remember, once a Pokémon isŇtransfered, it CANNOT be returned toŇthe Game Boy Game Pak.ȼSelect confirm once you’re ready, orŇselect cancel if you want to keep theŇPokémon on your Game Boy Game Pak.ƞ
PTGB.DIA_MYTHIC_CONVERT: It looks like you have a rareŇMythical Pokémon! Due to theirŇrarity, it seems they’ve overloadedŇthe machine.ȼI can stablize them if you’d like,Ňbut it’ll change some things like metŇlocation, OT, TID, and Shininess.ȼOtherwise I can leave them as is, butŇthere’s no guarentee that they’ll beŇtransferrable in the future. Do youŇwant me to stablize them?ȼThis will apply to all of theŇMythical Pokémon currently in yourŇbox.ƞ
PTGB.DIA_CANCEL: No worries! Feel free to come back ifŇyou change your mind! See you around!ƞ
PTGB.DIA_SOME_INVALID_PKMN: I see there is at least one PokémonŇthat cannot be transferred from yourŇcurrent box.ȼPokémon holding items or modifiedŇincorrectly through unintended meansŇcannot be transferred.ȼThe other Pokémon will transfer justŇfine though!ƞ
PTGB.DIA_MENU_BACK: No worries! Feel free to come backŇany time!ƞ
PTGB.DIA_IS_MISSINGNO: ... It seems like one of your PokémonŇis messing with the machine... ItŇlooks to only be graphical though, soŇwe can continue!ƞ
PTGB.DIA_ERROR_COLOSSEUM: It looks like you went to theŇcolosseum instead of the tradingŇroom! Let’s try that again!ƞ
PTGB.DIA_ERROR_COM_ENDED: Communication with the other deviceŇwas terminated. Let’s try that again!ƞ
PTGB.DIA_ERROR_DISCONNECT: It looks like the Game Boy Color linkŇcable was disconnected... Let’s tryŇthat again!ƞ
PTGB.DIA_ERROR_TIME_ONE: It looks like the connection timedŇout... Let’s try that again!ƞ
PTGB.DIA_ERROR_TIME_TWO: It seems like the connection timedŇout... Let’s try that again!ƞ
PTGB.DIA_WHAT_LANG_EVENT: What language is the Game Boy PokémonŇgame that you want to send an eventŇto?ƞ
PTGB.DIA_WHAT_GAME_EVENT: And which Game Boy Pokémon game doŇyou want to send an event to?ƞ
PTGB.DIA_K_DEX_NOT_FULL: Sorry trainer, it looks like youŇhaven’t caught all 150 Pokémon fromŇthe Kanto region yet.ȼGo out and catch them all and thenŇwe’ll be able to send over the event!ƞ
PTGB.DIA_J_DEX_NOT_FULL: Sorry trainer, it looks like youŇhaven’t caught all 99 new PokémonŇfrom the Johto region yet.ȼGo out and catch them all and thenŇwe’ll be able to send over the event!ƞ
